      "section_path_text": "From the beginning",
      "level": 1,
      "ordinal": 3,
      "summary": "Following a year in which the Baltic Capesize Index reached its highest level since 2009, 2022 has unfortunately not kept the party going. It was a lacklustre start to the year as the Chinese holidays approached and the historic levels of Chinese congestion embarked on a sharp decline, falling from 19.7m dwt to just 5.1m in little over a month.",
